'''James Anderson''' is an [[United States|American]] [[television writer]] and [[actor]]. Since 2000, he has served as a writer for [[NBC]]'s ''[[Saturday Night Live]]''. Anderson recently played himself on an episode of the network's  series ''[[30 Rock]]''.

